{
  "texts": [
    "Some of the hyperparameter optimization methods include Grid Search, Random Search and Bayesian optimization among others.",
    "Recent advances in Explainable Artificial Intelligence or XAI are aimed at making Intrusion Detection Systems more transparent and interpretable.",
    "The sub-discipline of machine learning and deep learning produces models, which delivers high accuracy but it is challenging to comprehend and trust the output due to the blackbox nature of these models 10.",
    "Interpretations of the model's predictions can then be made using XAI methods such as LIME or SHAP, and therein explaining the thought-process.",
    "In this way, due to the ability of observing the intrusion warning thoughts, security analysts are able to consider occurrences and set various security plans."
  ]
}